    <div class="column card-cont">
        <div class="card">
            <img src="https://pm1.narvii.com/5645/735dd555376a71c2ad2fcd7fc1d0cc71ad7fd9e0_00.jpg" alt="Mike" class="card-img">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Eiichiro Oda</h2>
                <p class="MostFamousWork">One Piece</p>
                <p>
                    Eiichiro Oda ( born January 1, 1975) is a
                    Japanese manga artist and the creator of the series One Piece (1997–present).
                    With more than 516.6 million tankōbon copies in circulation worldwide,
                    One Piece is both the best-selling manga in history.
                </p>
                <h3> Follow Oda </h3>
                <a href="#" class="fa fa-facebook"></a>
